{"h5747fe90g9fe8g4ec6ga329g0e912ec8911e": ["...you're both twice as tall as me but have half the bloody backbone!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditBackInteraction_Spotted.html", "a10225b9-cd33-58bf-e508-4e69ccd4de92"], "hca1137ddg0532g476dg89b7g35ac12c74f43": ["Whoever was flying that thing can't have survived - whatever's left is up for grabs!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditBackInteraction_Spotted.html", "a55d867d-eeae-acc7-b465-cfd73393481f"], "h89fdc8d6g0189g4851g8d94g3e6829ab48b1": ["<i>Look out! </i>Someone's comin' from the crypt!", "fa1a1fbd-2152-40e4-b53d-29e95d54279e", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditBackInteraction_Spotted.html", "7085a607-c094-f7d9-985d-8b958e9540a1"], "hc7334833gb229g49afga020gfc87faf4d899": ["<i>Look out! </i>Someone's comin' from the crypt!", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditBackInteraction_Spotted.html", "47431c91-3a78-9f0f-e6ca-b12045abb376"], "h9b701faagdd7cg40c0g8cbbga6d971c1526d": ["<i>Look out! </i>Someone's comin' from the crypt!", "0f4300f6-0e1e-4d6c-a582-5da588d64ea7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditBackInteraction_Spotted.html", "276ece0a-a093-631d-ae15-cc2df975e113"], "h28af3360g9932g4b41gaec4gdbbfe7b49626": ["What the - who're you?! That crypt's ours; think you can clear it out from under our noses?", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditBackInteraction_Spotted.html", "d30b2bac-63bb-6271-c176-9b9ea31be925"], "h9d92850eg1ed5g4598g9770gf2bbfe0d6aec": ["Now we're going to - <i>wait! </i>Who're you? And how did you get in there?!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditBackInteraction_Spotted.html", "89d886fb-1475-deac-18d8-2d984f132aa1"], "hd54f992bg8400g421dg99e2g00f70c51e8a8": ["That crypt's ours - we've got people guarding it! Tryin' to off us a